			\forall n \in \mathbb{N}, \; \quad n \geq n_{0}\implies |L-a_{n}| \;{\color{red} \leq}
			\; \varepsilon.$

		\item $\displaystyle \forall \varepsilon \;{\color{red} \in (0,1)}, \; \exists
			n_{0}\in \mathbb{N}, \; \forall n \in \mathbb{N}, \; \quad n \geq n_{0}\implies
