	\frametitle{True or False -- Definition of series}

	Let $\displaystyle \sum_{n=0}^{\infty}a_{n}$ be a series. Let
	$\displaystyle \{ S_{n}\}_{n=0}^{\infty}$ be its partial-sum sequence.

